{"tid":61723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4日內第3宗 大馬9歲仔割包皮切甩龜頭駁唔番","createTime":"2016-12-31T12:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T01:33:35.000Z","uid":52013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"492350115000c8839e3cdaf91684898bee29b224","tid":61723,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T12:34:39.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞四日內發生第三宗割包皮手術意外，一名9歲男童的陰莖龜頭慘被切斷，無法駁回。<br />\n<br />\n受害男童日前由家人帶往一家診所做割包皮手術，醫生使用剪刀進行手術時，意外把男童的龜頭切斷，僅剩少許皮肉相連。雖然男童被急送醫院進行接駁手術，但抵步時陰莖已發黑，需要切除。<br />\n代表男童的律師說，男童9歲便遭遇如此悲劇，政府有必要關注割禮手術的程序和安全，以免悲劇再次發生。<br />\n在本周二，一名10歲男童進行激光割包皮手術時，龜頭亦遭切斷，幸而接駁手術成功，可保住陰莖。居於古晉另一名10歲男童在接受割禮手術時，陰莖亦被切斷2.5公分，家人已向醫生提出民事索償。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161231/56113513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161231%2F56113513&d=pxl3izJNkSXnyjQjIDpCg2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=47a2ba9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161231%2F56113513&h=92df391d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161231/56113513</a>"},{"pid":"d697e0b7988844aee94de4358ddfc99a0b69ed19","tid":61723,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161231/56113513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161231%2F56113513&d=pxl3izJNkSXnyjQjIDpCg2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=47a2ba9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161231%2F56113513&h=92df391d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161231/56113513</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"85ee0013908bf12bc2b1a5e06173b4c27413d6f4","tid":61723,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T12:37:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9bdb907075e5d5e1d8dda2190405641ba3f69bc","tid":61723,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T12:55:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>變做女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曾經滄海"},{"pid":"55d4c6d798d84a22c9af99a2860c782e4e8b21df","tid":61723,"uid":20670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T14:07:39.000Z","msg":"變埋性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9c48c883b73070cc3655fa680ebe8378af5af7","tid":61723,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T01:33:35.000Z","msg":"佢嘅人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}